            <title>[LUDOC-279] Add commands leading to setxattr to the doc/protocol document</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-279</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The shell command &apos;setfattr&apos; issues a non-POSIX system call&lt;br/&gt;
&apos;setxattr()&apos; which results in a call to &apos;ll_setxattr()&apos; in&lt;br/&gt;
lustre/llite/xattr.c.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Document the messages exchanged to carry out this operation as well as&lt;br/&gt;
any state change that it can cause.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
